# Alpha Wolf Wrap Studio — CODEOWNERS
#
# Path-scoped ownership protecting ADR-0013 deploy-infrastructure invariants
# and security-critical auth primitives. A PR touching any path below REQUIRES
# @archerverified's review before merge — even when CodeRabbit reports clean.
#
# Why path-scoped (no global `*` catch-all):
#   The autonomous /goal chain (Goals 1-4) opens and auto-merges many PRs after
#   CI passes. A global catch-all would gate EVERY PR on a human review and stall
#   the chain. Scoping ownership to the load-bearing + security paths keeps the
#   chain moving while still forcing a human (Archer) onto the changes that can
#   silently re-break the deploy or weaken auth.
#
# This file supersedes the prior root /CODEOWNERS (which only set `* @archerverified`
# but was never enforced — branch protection had require_code_owner_reviews=false).
# GitHub resolves a single CODEOWNERS file by precedence (.github/ > / > docs/), so
# the root copy is removed to avoid a misleading dead file.
#
# Re-apply / audit references:
#   /docs/adr/0013-deploy-infrastructure-contract.md  (the invariants protected here)
#   /docs/setup/github-branch-protection.json         (the protection payload that enforces this)
#   /docs/setup/manual-steps.md                       (operator runbook)
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners

# ── ADR-0013 deploy-infrastructure invariants ──────────────────────────────
/apps/web/next.config.ts                   @archerverified
/render.yaml                               @archerverified
/packages/db/prisma/schema.prisma          @archerverified
/packages/db/prisma/sql/*.sql              @archerverified
/.coderabbit.yaml                          @archerverified
/docs/adr/0013-*                           @archerverified
/apps/web/package.json                     @archerverified

# ── Security-critical auth primitives ──────────────────────────────────────
/packages/auth/src/csrf*                   @archerverified
/packages/auth/src/password*               @archerverified
/packages/auth/src/otp*                    @archerverified
/apps/web/middleware.ts                    @archerverified

# ── This ownership policy guards itself ────────────────────────────────────
/.github/CODEOWNERS                        @archerverified
